269
00:24:41,179 --> 00:24:44,910
<i>"And doing more with less is,</i>
<i>in a word, Mr. Bandini,</i>

270
00:24:45,016 --> 00:24:46,984
<i>"what writing is all about."</i>

271
00:25:06,004 --> 00:25:07,471
Still mad at me?

272
00:25:08,607 --> 00:25:10,040
Not that I know of.

273
00:25:11,076 --> 00:25:13,010
