to order something?

274
00:25:14,279 --> 00:25:17,009
A cigar. Something from Havana.

275
00:25:18,383 --> 00:25:19,975
They're a quarter.

276
00:25:24,556 --> 00:25:26,148
Keep the change.

277
00:25:41,973 --> 00:25:45,136
-I said keep the change.
-Not from you.

278
00:25:45,777 --> 00:25:47,142
You're poor.

279
00:25:57,989 --> 00:25:59,854
Don't I look different?

280
