You've changed.

286
00:26:29,654 --> 00:26:31,588
Before you were just mean.

287
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:35,626
Now that you've got a couple of bucks,
you're mean and stuck-up.

288
00:26:36,595 --> 00:26:37,960
Forty cents.

289
00:26:38,229 --> 00:26:39,753
Well, you haven't changed.

290
00:26:39,864 --> 00:26:41,957
You're just the same little
Mexican princess,

291
00:26:42,067 --> 00:26:44,592
-charming and innocent.
-I'm not charming and I'm not innocent.

292
00:26:44,703 --> 00:26:47,934
To me you'll always be a sweet
