Cows eat nothing but weeds.

423
00:38:59,570 --> 00:39:02,562
Dead weeds. Meat's full of worms.

424
00:39:03,274 --> 00:39:06,801
They paint it to look bloody and red.
Did you know that?

425
00:39:07,812 --> 00:39:09,473
Maybe you could use that
in one of your...

426
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:11,480
Okay, okay. What do you need?

427
00:39:11,582 --> 00:39:14,346
Fifty cents? There's a butcher on Olive.

428
00:39:14,652 --> 00:39:17,712
He's got the real McCoy,
beef from Kansas City.

429
00:39:18,222 --> 00:39:20,986
It would help keep me off the hard stuff.

430
00:39:28,332 --> 00:39:30,630
I'll make it good with you, kid.

431
00:39:35,339 --> 00:39:37,807
I'll pay you back 1,000 times.

432
00:39:43,948 --> 00:39:45,939
<i>I had just under $10.</i>

433
00:39:46,417 --> 00:39:48,408
