<i>or two pairs of pants</i>

435
00:39:52,056 --> 00:39:55,583
<i>or 1,000 postage stamps</i>
<i>to send stories to Mencken.</i>

436
00:39:57,595 --> 00:40:00,359
<i>But you don't have any stories or talent.</i>

437
00:40:04,168 --> 00:40:08,366
"Don't stop. Don't stop.
Please don't ever stop."

438
00:40:10,107 --> 00:40:11,335
Garbage.

439
00:40:40,171 --> 00:40:42,435
Camilla. Camilla, wait up.

440
00:40:42,973 --> 00:40:46,101
